snippet.title: Enderal Expansion: Forgotten Stories - Mood Teaser
snippet.description:
Download this free modification for Skyrim directly via Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/933480/Enderal_Forgotten_Stories/
https://sureai.net

A small teaser showing some impressions of the new story content to be added in the "Forgotten Stories"-DLC for Enderal.

Voice actors in this video (in order of appearance): River Kanoff, Lani Minella, Gabriel Wolf, Kristyn Mass, Heather Jane Hogan, Jessica Osborne, Dave Fennoy, Sarah Dawe
